---
layout: draft
title: Philosophy & Co.
date: '2015-08-09 11:21:54'
---


[**Language, Identity and Multiculturalism**](http://www.amazon.de/Language-Identity-Multiculturalism-Gabriel-Furmuzachi/dp/3832516794/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&s=books-intl-de&qid=1244803878&sr=8-1) - a book on language acquisition and use and its importance in shaping one's identity. Published with LOGOS in 2007.

[**Emotions, Metaphors and Reality**](http://cento.red/emotions-metaphors-and-reality/) - my Canadian MA, (theoretically) dealing with the (rather slim) body of work of William Lyall and actually focusing on a theory of emotions (thank you, Sartre) and a theory of metaphors (thank you, Ricoeur). 

[**Reason and Nature**](http://cento.red/reason-and-nature-a-canadian-perspective/) - on William Lyall, again. 

[**Metaphysics and Experience**](http://cento.red/metafizica-si-experienta/) - in Romanian. A humble beginning, nevertheless. 

[**The Intolerable Acts**](http://cento.red/the-intolerable-acts/) - care for a tiny bit of American history? 

[**The Prince or The Cobbler**](http://cento.red/the-prince-or-the-cobbler/)? - an identity story, Locke style. 

[**Butler vs. Locke**](http://cento.red/butler-vs-locke/) - identity revisited. 

[**Philosophical Counsels**](http://cento.red/philosophical-counsels/) - old piece. Psychoanalysis vs. philosophy.  

[**Sfaturi Filosofice**](http://cento.red/sfaturi-filosofice/) - in Romanian. The same as above. 

[**The Concept of Tragic in Romanian Philosophy**](http://cento.red/the-concept-of-tragic-in-romanian-philosophy/) - Rosca, Liiceanu & Cioran.  

[**Physics and Philosophy**](http://cento.red/physics-and-philosophy/) - Heisenberg's uncertainty principle (quite an old piece). 

[**On God and Dispensations**](http://cento.red/on-god-and-dispensations/) - almost hilarious. 

[**Fragments**](http://cento.red/ginduri-intrerupte/) - in Romanian. Actually, not that bad. 

[**The Barber – The Man Mho Wasn’t There**](http://cento.red/the-barber/) - film and philosophy. 

[**Being John Malkovich: postmodern identity tricks**](http://cento.red/being-john-malkovich-post-modern-identity-tricks/) - film and philosophy again. 

[**Körperwelten**](http://cento.red/korperwelten/) - the art of science vs. the science of art
